<note n="0430003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0430003">鈕＝紐【宋】【元】【宮】，＝細【明】</note>
<note n="0431003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0431003"><g ref="#CB00950">󰎶</g>＝揁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】＊</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div type="taisho-notes">
<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0427009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0427009">聖本首缺</note>
<note n="0428001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0428001">意＝喜【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0428002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0428002">作＝畜【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0428003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0428003">膩＝<g ref="#CB01882">𧸐</g>【宋】【元】【宮】</note>
<note n="0428004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0428004">利＝<g ref="#CB02185">𠮧</g>【宮】</note>
<note n="0428005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0428005">雇＝顧【明】</note>
<note n="0428006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0428006">時＝得【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0428007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0428007">汝字以上聖本斷缺</note>
<note n="0429001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429001">揵＝健【宋】【聖】，犍【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0429002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429002">椎＝稚【宋】【元】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0429003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429003">覩波＝堵波【三】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0429004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429004">列＝到【聖】＊</note>
<note n="0429005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429005">礦＝獷【聖】</note>
<note n="0429006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429006">挂＝掛【宋】【明】【宮】，桂【聖】</note>
<note n="0429007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429007">釘＝丁【聖】＊</note>
<note n="0429008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429008">〔應〕－【聖】</note>
<note n="0429009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429009">不＋（應）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0429010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429010">摒＝屏【三】【宮】【聖】＊</note>
<note n="0429011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429011">潔＝繫【聖】</note>
<note n="0429012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429012">先＝無【聖】</note>
<note n="0429013" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0429013">以＝此【宋】【宮】</note>
<note n="0430001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0430001">〔尼陀那〕－【三】【宮】【聖】</note>
<note n="0430002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0430002">損＝揁【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0430003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0430003">鈕＝紐【宋】【元】【宮】，細【明】</note>
<note n="0430004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0430004">乏＝之【聖】</note>
<note n="0430005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0430005">恚＝苾【明】</note>
<note n="0430006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0430006">凌＝陵【聖】</note>
<note n="0430007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0430007">諸＝詣【聖】</note>
<note n="0430008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0430008">禾＝來【聖】</note>
<note n="0430009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0430009">伽＝迦【宋】【宮】</note>
<note n="0430010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0430010">若＝共【宮】</note>
<note n="0431001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0431001">准＝唯【宋】</note>
<note n="0431002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0431002">剃＝削【宮】</note>
<note n="0431003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0431003"><g ref="#CB00950">󰎶</g>＝揁【三】【宮】【聖】＊</note>
<note n="0431004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0431004">此下聖本有光明皇后願文</note>
<note n="0431005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0431005">部＋（律）【聖】</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
